<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-118720" number="36451" version="1506">
			<HEADING>Chapter 58: Notification of Mold Remediation</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-15826" name="T15C058"/>Chapter 58: Notification of Mold Remediation</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-114302" number="36452" version="1408">
								<HEADING>§ 58-01 Applicability</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-15830" name="T15C058_58-01"/>§ 58-01 Applicability</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114308" number="36453" version="2512">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>This rule applies to mold remediation projects for which a notification to the department of environmental protection is required pursuant to § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="24-154" destination-id="0-0-0-0">24-154</LINK> of the Administrative Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114307" number="36454" version="1408">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/19/2019, eff. 4/18/2019) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-114309" number="36455" version="1408">
								<HEADING>§ 58-02 Conditions that Pose an Immediate Threat of Harm to Any Person or Damage to Property.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-15828" name="T15C058_58-02"/>§ 58-02 Conditions that Pose an Immediate Threat of Harm to Any Person or Damage to Property.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114306" number="36456" version="1821">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>To determine if a notification of mold remediation must be filed, pursuant to § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="24-154" destination-id="0-0-0-0">24-154</LINK> of the Administrative Code, an immediate risk of harm to any person or damage to property is considered to exist when any of the following are present in the dwelling to be remediated: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114305" number="36457" version="1408">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>At least 30 square feet or more of visible mold within one room. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114310" number="36458" version="1408">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Excessive water accumulation or flooding. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114304" number="36459" version="1408">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Before commencing work, the mold remediation contractor must determine if any of the conditions listed in subdivision (a) exist, and must indicate in the mold remediation notice which, if any of these conditions exist, and attach appropriate documentation of said condition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-114303" number="36460" version="1611">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/19/2019, eff. 4/18/2019) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-036]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>